					<span class="ft-wordmark">fullstack<strong>hero</strong></span>
				</a>
				<p class="ft-tagline">Open-source .NET starter kit for teams that ship.</p>
				<div class="ft-socials">
					<a href="https://github.com/fullstackhero/dotnet-starter-kit" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="GitHub">
