					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="ft-col">
				<h5>Documentation</h5>
				<a href="/dotnet-starter-kit/introduction/">Introduction</a>
				<a href="/dotnet-starter-kit/quick-start/">Quick Start</a>
				<a href="/dotnet-starter-kit/architecture/">Architecture</a>
				<a href="/dotnet-starter-kit/adding-a-feature/">Add a Feature</a>
			</div>
			<div class="ft-col">
				<h5>Modules</h5>
				<a href="/dotnet-starter-kit/modules/identity/">Identity</a>
				<a href="/dotnet-starter-kit/modules/multitenancy/">Multitenancy</a>
				<a href="/dotnet-starter-kit/modules/auditing/">Auditing</a>
				<a href="/dotnet-starter-kit/building-blocks/">Building Blocks</a>
			</div>
			<div class="ft-col">
				<h5>Community</h5>
				<a href="https://github.com/fullstackhero/dotnet-starter-kit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/fullstackhero/dotnet-starter-kit/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Issues</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/fullstackhero/dotnet-starter-kit/discussions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discussions</a>
				<a href="/dotnet-starter-kit/contributing/">Contributing</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="ft-bottom">
			<span>MIT License. Built with care by the fullstackhero community.</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.ft { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg-card); }
	.ft-in {
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.ft-top {
		display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem; padding: 3rem 0 2.5rem;
	}

	.ft-brand {
		display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.ft-logo { width: 32px !important; height: 32px !important; border-radius: 6px; }
	.ft-wordmark { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
	.ft-wordmark strong { font-weight: 700; }

	.ft-tagline { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-faint); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

	.ft-socials { display: flex; gap: 0.25rem; }
	.ft-socials a {
		display: grid; place-items: center; width: 2rem; height: 2rem;
		border-radius: 6px; color: var(--text-faint);
		transition: color .15s, background .15s;
	}
	.ft-socials a:hover { color: var(--text-dim); background: rgba(128,128,128,0.06); }

	.ft-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
	.ft-col h5 {
		font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		color: var(--text-faint); margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}
	.ft-col a {
		font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-dim);
		transition: color .15s;
	}
	.ft-col a:hover { color: var(--text); }

	.ft-bottom {
		padding: 1.5rem 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
		font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-faint);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.ft-in { padding: 0 1rem; }
		.ft-top {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem; padding: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
			text-align: center;
		}
		.ft-brand-col {
			display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
		}
		.ft-brand { justify-content: center; }
		.ft-tagline { text-align: center; }
		.ft-socials { justify-content: center; }
		.ft-col { align-items: center; }
		.ft-col h5 { text-align: center; }
		.ft-bottom { text-align: center; }
	}
</style>
